{"lastModified":1751914955139,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::60151f50-ab38-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia, Italy\n\nCANADOS 72. Crewed yacht charter in Sardinia. The Canados 72 is a prestigious boat with elegant lines that conveys luxury and quality. Externally we have a magnificent Flybridge that dominates the boat with a large table that comfortably accommodates eight people, a large awning, comfortable cushions and an outdoor kitchen. The wide bow is completed by unparalleled cushions that will lull you under the sun's rays. Below deck we find four comfortable suites each with its own bathroom. We have a fabulous master cabin with a king-size double bed and en-suite bathroom with shower cubicle and an incredible VIP cabin with en suite bathroom. In addition, there are two other spacious cabins (one of which is triple) both equipped with a bathroom with shower. The layout is completed by a dinette with breathtaking spaces, with a large dining table, and a spacious galley located amidships, with everything you need to prepare haute cuisine dishes. On our Canados 72 you will be welcomed by an experienced and professional crew who will be able to cope with all your needs. An enviable charter yacht, equipped with options such as generator, air conditioning, water toys and a crew cabin with bathroom and independent access.","blueprint":{"name":"CANADOS 72","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::60151f50-ab38-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::a6f4e731-ab3c-11ef-b930-b5199fea62b3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::60151f50-ab38-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::a6f905e0-ab3c-11ef-b930-b5199fea62b3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::60151f50-ab38-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::a6f47200-ab3c-11ef-8335-c3af5c2a6322/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::60151f50-ab38-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::a6f97b10-ab3c-11ef-b930-b5199fea62b3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel